extends layout.pug

block content

  nav.nav
    a(href='/')
      span &larr;
      |  Back

  article.portfolio-about
    .inner-wrapper.flex-row-wrap.two-col
      .about-intro-box.box

        //- Replace with your name
        h1 Andrew Whatmore

        //- Feel free to personalize the title below
        p Full Stack JavaScript Developer


        .about-bio

          p 
            | Do you require secure app or website development?
            br
            br
            | Hi, I'm Andrew, and I am a Full Stack JavaScript Developer. Whether you require front-end, back-end or both, developing JavaScript apps is my hobby.
            br
            br
            | Security is paramount, which is why I am certified by IMB in Application Security for Developers to make sure your apps are secure. 
            br
            br
            | I have also been developing WordPress websites since 2021. This experience includes the development and management of eCommerce, subscriptions, email marketing, advertising, GDPR, and SEO.
            br
            br
            | I also completed Harvard University's famous CS50 course.


      .skills-contact-box.box
        h6 Skills

        //- Replace skills below with your own skills — at this point, you should be able to list as many as ten skills
        ul
          li HTML
          li CSS
          li JavaScript
          li Git and GitHub
          li VS Code
          li Accessibility
          li OOP
          li Fetch and Public APIs
          li Node.js
          li Express
          li Pug
          li SEO

        h6 Contact Info

        //- Replace with your own contact info - feel free to use fake information if you prefer
        ul
          li 555-555-1234
          li boffwareweb@gmail.com

        //- Add URLs to the hrefs below to link to your social media accounts - feel free to use non-personal links to social media home pages if you prefer
        a.btn-link(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/andrew-w-5441b5167/') LinkedIn
        a.btn-link(href='https://github.com/hagbeb') GitHub
        a.btn-link(href='https://x.com/home') Twitter

    nav.nav
      a(href='/')
        span &larr;
        |  Back